      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\tB2C, B2B跟H5一样是中式英语。楼主显然搞反了BC的意思。<br/>\n<br/>\n他自己也说了，台积电鸿海是to business. 宏基微星是 to consumer. 不知道为什么还问出这种莫名其妙的问题。显然是两者都有。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2024-01-16",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "720651",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "spark808",
        "uid": "9787"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t是不是搞混了？<br/>\n<br/>\n鸿海、台积电、和硕都是Business to Business.<br/>\n宏碁是Business to Consumer.<br/>\n士林夜市是 Consumer to Consumer.<br/>\n<br/>\n台湾2300万人口，世界500强有7、8家吧，可以了。中国大陆14亿人，世界500强130家左右，而且大部分是垄断国企。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2024-01-16",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "720657",
      "is_folded": false,
